snippet: Dave & Buster's Entertainment has declared game over for latest effort to go public, announcing on Thursday that it was withdrawing its planned initial stock sale because of "continued volatility" in the markets.
abstract: Dave & Buster's Entertainment has declared game over for latest effort to go public, announcing on Thursday that it was withdrawing its planned initial stock sale because of "continued volatility" in the markets.

headline.main: Dave & Buster's Calls Off Its I.P.O.
